<table><tr><td>Scottish Intercollegiate Guidelines Network (SIGN). Glaucoma referral and safe discharge. A national clinical guideline. Edinburgh (Scotland): Scottish Intercollegiate Guidelines Network (SIGN); 2015 Mar. 38 p.&nbsp;(SIGN publication; no. 144).&nbsp; [72 references]</td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712205450/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=49634&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252fwww.sign.ac.uk%252fpdf%252fSIGN144.pdf">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712205450im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
