                        <h3><a href="#">Financial Disclosures/Conflicts of Interest</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>All members of the guideline development group made declarations of interest. A register of interests is available in the supporting material section for this guideline at <a href="/web/20180712205450/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=49634&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=http%3a%2f%2fwww.sign.ac.uk" title="SIGN Web site">www.sign.ac.uk</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712205450im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>.</p></div></p>
